WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Chapter 9
In their underwear!

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.980
How lovely they sound! Like little nightingales.

00:00:15.980 --> 00:00:19.400
You have done a great job with the choir, Sister Juana. 

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:22.460
There is no doubt that we’re going to win the Yotutepec festival.

00:00:22.660 --> 00:00:24.640
Winning is not the most important part, Father Beto. 

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:25.720
The real prize…

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:28.520
Juanita! Be careful with the B flat… 

00:00:29.360 --> 00:00:32.040
The real prize is going  to sing, Father Beto.

00:00:32.300 --> 00:00:34.880
We’re going to win the Yotutepec festival!

00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:36.380
Oh, No!

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:37.960
What’s going on, Richi?

00:00:38.180 --> 00:00:39.820
I had better pull over and check.

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:42.800
What is wrong? 

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:44.880
It has a lot of parts.

00:00:45.080 --> 00:00:45.880
Oh, my God!

00:00:45.880 --> 00:00:49.340
Father Beto! There is a pond down here. 

00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:50.280
Would you like to come?

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:52.680
I want this cursed thing to be fixed.

00:00:53.980 --> 00:00:55.920
Van of the devil!

00:00:56.060 --> 00:00:59.000
Let's go children, Father Beto is not in the mood for swimming. 

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:01.780
Work…

00:01:03.660 --> 00:01:05.360
Oh, my God! 

00:01:09.140 --> 00:01:10.920
What is going on here?

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:14.920
Father Beto! The children really wanted to swim

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:16.440
 and I couldn’t refuse.

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:19.080
But Sister Juana, they are in their underwear!

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:20.400
What is wrong with that?

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.600
You can see their backsides! 

00:01:22.600 --> 00:01:25.740
How can you permit such a degree of indecency? 

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:29.040
Please don’t make the children feel ashamed of their bodies, Father Beto. 

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.960
One’s body is the temple of God. 

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:33.520
You can’t go around showing it off just like that.

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:35.600
It encourages wicked thoughts. 

00:01:35.720 --> 00:01:38.860
You are the one with the wicked thoughts, Father Beto. 

00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:41.140
These children aren’t offending God in any way.

00:01:41.140 --> 00:01:42.500
That is enough! 

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:46.400
Children, get out of the water right now!

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:51.340
Father Beto, please let us splash around for a little longer!

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:55.320
The choir of the San Pablo Parish does not splash around. 

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:58.260
The parish choir will have its say, Father Beto...

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:02.040
The body is not in opposition to the spirit

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.880
both are the creation of God. 

00:02:04.100 --> 00:02:07.520
Any person who despises the body also despises its creator. 

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:11.040
God gave us the human body with all its feelings

00:02:11.040 --> 00:02:13.480
not to deny them, but to live them. 

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:15.680
Enjoyment is not a sin!

00:02:16.540 --> 00:02:19.060
So… what do you think, Father Beto?

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:23.280
You immodest children! Get dressed! Straightaway!

00:02:23.740 --> 00:02:26.300
You will regret this, Father Beto.

00:02:26.420 --> 00:02:28.780
Never! Get in the van!

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:39.520
On the shore...

00:02:39.520 --> 00:02:44.040
 I left my boat...

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:46.920
Next to you…

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:53.320
I will find out which one of you clowns played this trick.

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:56.180
Well, we already know who it was.

00:02:56.900 --> 00:02:58.100
Step on it, Richi.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.000
To be continued...

